    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aryballoi of the later style, having a relatively tall shape with a more pointed base than the globular or spherical styles. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
